statements: SELECT * FROM telecardiology_outcomes
SELECT patient_id, age, gender FROM telecardiology_outcomes
SELECT diagnosis, treatment_protocol, outcome FROM telecardiology_outcomes
SELECT patient_id, age, gender, diagnosis, treatment_protocol, outcome FROM telecardiology_outcomes WHERE age > 40
SELECT * FROM telecardiology_outcomes WHERE diagnosis = 'Hypertension'
SELECT patient_id, age, gender, diagnosis, treatment_protocol, outcome FROM telecardiology_outcomes WHERE gender = 'Male' ORDER BY age DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT age, COUNT(*) AS patient_count FROM telecardiology_outcomes GROUP BY age HAVING patient_count > 1 ORDER BY patient_count DESC, age ASC;
